Share this on WhatsAppSpread the lovePresidential campaign posters of Rivers Governor Nyesom Wike of Rivers State have been sighted in some areas of the Federal Capital Territory, Abuja.
Sighted on Monday at some traffic kiosks along airports road, Asokoro and the Federal Secretariat., the posters bear: Here to serve 2023: Barr Ezenwo Nyesom Wike for president.
The Northerners For Change Group are the promoters.
The PDP governor has only been speculated to e running as the sidekick of his Sokoto colleague Aminu Tambuwal.
Wike has yet to declare his intention either.
